---
title: Creamy Chicken, Leek & Veggie Risoni with Roasted Kumara & Parmesan
description: What’s going into the risoni today? A little bit of leek, a heap of roasted kumara, a touch of capsicum and courgette, and finally a sprinkling of herby seasoning. It’s a perfect concoction of flavour, texture and pure yumminess.

